By Chris Swaim ,
16 hours ago Sunny skies are back for the weekend! Temperatures will be even feeling summer-like. Sunday for example will be at or above 80Â°! There is some potential for fog into Sunday morning. Another cold front comes through early next week. That could fire off some showers overnight, but we look to clear out on Monday. It will be much colder next week with highs in the 60s and 50!
